original: Jörnstedt, Anna Matilda, rektor, Karlskrona, f. 20/10/92 i Uddevalla. — Ex. v. h. lär :nesem. v. stift. Kjellbergska flicksk. i Gbg 13. Res. t. bl. a. Engl., Tyskl. o. Frankr. Vik. ämneslär. v. Kalmar elem:sk. f. fl. 13-14, ord. ämneslär. v. Karlskrona h. flicK-lärov. 14-33, tf. förest, där 33-34, ord. ämnesilär. o. rektor v. Karlskrona komm. flicksk. sed. 34. Sekr. i styr. f. nämnda skola, led. av styr. f. folk-sk. o. fortsättn :sk., v. ordf. i Fredr.-Bremer-förb. Karlskrona-krets o. i RPO lokalavd. i Karlskrona, led. av styr. f. Karlskrona allm. djurskydds-fören. SvRKSM.
translated: Jörnstedt, Anna Matilda, principal, Karlskrona, b. 20/10/92 in Uddevalla. - Graduated from teacher training at Kjellbergska girls' school in Gothenburg in 1913. Traveled to England, Germany, and France. Substitute subject teacher at Kalmar elementary school and others from 1913-1914, regular subject teacher at Karlskrona girls' high school from 1914-1933, acting principal there from 1933-1934, regular subject teacher and principal at Karlskrona municipal girls' school since 1934. Secretary of the board for the mentioned school, board member of the people's school and continuing education school, vice-chair of the Fredr.-Bremer Association Karlskrona branch and the RPO local chapter in Karlskrona, board member of the Karlskrona general animal protection association (SvRKSM).
